<Layout
	title="Editorial"
	description="The editorial method of Global South News prioritizes source mapping, development context and practical clarity."
	pubDate={new Date('2026-05-16T13:00:00Z')}
>
	<p>
		Global South News begins from a practical premise: the world cannot be understood only from
		the old Atlantic center. Trade routes, public banks, industrial policy, energy systems,
		science, infrastructure and diplomacy are being reorganized across the Global South.
	</p>

	<p>
		Our coverage follows institutions, corridors, ports, railways, currencies, food systems and
		regional forums that shape the lives of billions of people.
	</p>

	<p>
		The first duty is orientation: what changed, who benefits, who resists and what remains
		uncertain. Every story is built from understood sources, with clear attribution and
		development context.
	</p>
</Layout>
